Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.36,0:00:08.15,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,搅拌搅拌搅拌搅拌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.40,0:00:11.49,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,把聚谷氨酸切开破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.57,0:00:13.74,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,变成谷氨酸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.20,0:00:16.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,龙的真髓就是破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.82,0:00:17.74,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,已经可以了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.78,0:00:18.45,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,还要搅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.87,0:00:21.79,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林  早安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.12,0:00:23.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,早上好  小林
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.54,0:00:24.08,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.17,0:00:24.79,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.25,0:00:28.88,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,今天是很有夏天感觉的  加了秋葵的味增汤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.88,0:00:30.88,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.09,0:00:35.55,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,之后好像要办祭典对吧  阿竹跟我说了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.05,0:00:39.01,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,对  我和才川约好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.18,0:00:40.22,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你们要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.52,0:00:43.48,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,听说会有很多小摊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.48,0:01:31.19,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,泷谷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.23,0:01:34.69,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,当人际关系变得沉重的时候  你会怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.32,0:01:37.70,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.03,0:01:40.91,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,应该会随遇而安吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.08,0:01:43.87,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.12,0:01:49.33,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.93,0:02:00.18,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,今早好像提到过这个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.93,0:02:02.72,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,要不要和托尔一起去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.14,0:02:05.23,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,浴衣的话  去买吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.85,0:02:07.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,虽然我可不会穿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:11.11,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,已经开始装饰了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.36,0:02:16.19,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托尔  为什么她在这
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.40,0:02:19.49,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,商店街的人拜托我来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.28,0:02:22.62,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,他们很信任你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.03,0:02:25.08,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,虽然我不知道祭典是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.20,0:02:26.41,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是还挺麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.62,0:02:27.37,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.54,0:02:28.41,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我看你挺开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.08,0:02:31.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,因为小林你会从那经过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.75,0:02:34.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,一想到由我负责安放的灯笼会照耀小林我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.26,0:02:36.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\pos(1019,985.333)}私  心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.26,0:02:36.21,Kobayashi S2 - Comment,,0,0,0,,注：日语中“诗意”和“私心”谐音。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.26,0:02:36.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,还真有诗意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.88,0:02:38.26,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你在那天有什么安排吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.72,0:02:41.26,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,女仆咖啡厅的人好像想开店
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.43,0:02:43.26,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我应该会去帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.89,0:02:49.94,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,最近托尔好像做得很不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.15,0:02:53.52,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,积极地和镇上的人接触
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.07,0:02:56.40,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,帮助他们  然后构筑信任关系
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.94,0:02:58.24,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,因为她完美地满足了他们的需求
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.11,0:03:02.12,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,拥有龙的力量要办到这些应该不难吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:05.83,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我认为这是非常好的变化
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:07.45,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.37,0:03:11.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是我不禁重新思考
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.96,0:03:15.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我真的是值得这样的托尔仰慕的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.67,0:03:17.88,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不  不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.05,0:03:23.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,只是因为她不给我添麻烦而有点寂寞了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.18,0:03:28.22,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这种想法还是埋藏心底吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.86,0:03:43.36,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我想要这件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.32,0:03:45.24,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,很可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.58,0:03:46.49,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:48.91,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林  这件怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.58,0:03:51.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我觉得很适合伊露露你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.41,0:03:52.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.62,0:03:54.88,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林不穿浴衣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:03:57.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我就不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.42,0:03:58.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.55,0:04:00.09,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你觉得哪件好看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.72,0:04:02.59,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,选托尔自己喜欢的就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.01,0:04:05.68,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我想要小林帮我选
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.97,0:04:07.72,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.97,0:04:13.73,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,听天由命点兵点将点到谁就选谁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.02,0:04:14.65,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好  这件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.44,0:04:19.48,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我才不要听天由命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.78,0:04:20.57,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我要选这件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.69,0:04:21.11,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.54,0:04:34.33,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你很兴奋啊  艾尔玛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.50,0:04:36.50,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我最喜欢祭典了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.09,0:04:38.63,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那边的祭典是什么样的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.25,0:04:40.55,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我想一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.71,0:04:43.01,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,烤乳猪  蒸鸭肉…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.09,0:04:44.93,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就只记得吃的了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.89,0:04:47.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,发现托尔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:50.72,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,谢谢惠顾  这是您要的女仆咖啡店特制蛋包饭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:52.23,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托尔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.44,0:04:55.35,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你们来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.44,0:04:57.40,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,为什么不穿女仆装
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.44,0:04:59.94,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,而是像店长一样的纯黑打扮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.48,0:05:02.65,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,因为穿女仆装不方便活动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.78,0:05:04.45,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,还真敢说啊  你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.95,0:05:06.41,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,重要的是心意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.53,0:05:08.41,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,蛋包饭也给我一份
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.91,0:05:10.33,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好好排队去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.45,0:05:14.46,Kobayashi S2 - HandWrite,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\c&HBC9DF7&\bord2\3c&HF0F6FE&\pos(568.857,363.714)}队尾在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.16,0:05:14.62,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,人气还真旺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.33,0:05:17.29,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,在这里排队的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.46,0:05:20.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,没准就吃不到烤玉米烤鱿鱼大阪烧苹果糖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.34,0:05:22.76,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,以及其它很多东西了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:24.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:26.72,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,回去会帮你带一份的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.34,0:05:29.85,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真的吗  托尔你真是好人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.01,0:05:31.01,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这就哭了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.97,0:05:34.02,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我还有一小时就能下班了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.52,0:05:35.31,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.83,0:05:56.29,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这个酱油的风味真是让人无法抗拒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.46,0:05:57.58,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那还真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.04,0:05:59.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:01.67,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,露科亚  翔太
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:02.67,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.17,0:06:05.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,祭典果然很不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:06.26,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.93,0:06:08.84,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,虽然和那边不太一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.39,0:06:12.76,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那边的祭典一般是为了祭祀神明
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.06,0:06:16.56,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,最近日本这种意味已经越来越淡了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.85,0:06:20.40,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,办祭典时人类的防备会加强  龙也无法靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.65,0:06:25.24,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我记得北方的大国在春天会举办盛大的祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.61,0:06:28.03,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那时候可是很难过去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.20,0:06:30.07,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,听说神也会降临哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.07,0:06:31.91,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,她们说起老家的事就插不上嘴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.70,0:06:35.12,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,虽然听听异世界的事也很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.33,0:06:36.91,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是会给人一种疏远的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:39.58,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,还是忍住不说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.25,0:06:43.29,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.26,0:06:47.55,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,康娜  你那件浴衣真好看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.84,0:06:51.89,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,才川的浴衣也很好看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:06:59.02,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,康娜  明年也一起来逛祭典吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:06:59.89,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.69,0:07:02.73,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就算长大老去变成老婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.86,0:07:03.77,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,也要一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.49,0:07:09.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,才川  活得久一些
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.61,0:07:12.03,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我会的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.41,0:07:17.33,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,康娜和我永远是朋友  永远
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.59,0:07:25.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这里真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.46,0:07:26.80,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小孩子们都在笑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.34,0:07:29.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,明明你也很孩子气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:32.39,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是有时候又一副比我还年长的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.51,0:07:35.81,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,居然没掉下去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.35,0:07:40.23,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,阿竹  我是被骗了才留在这边的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.69,0:07:41.64,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,被骗了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.56,0:07:44.56,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,有人要我长大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.36,0:07:47.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我也觉得已经不能再当个孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.32,0:07:53.49,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是小林诱骗我说可以当回小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.24,0:07:59.87,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不过你也还是存在大人般成熟的一面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:01.25,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.50,0:08:02.71,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,如果是这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.75,0:08:04.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我也骗骗你好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.92,0:08:06.75,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我会让你能一直当个孩子的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:10.80,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.88,0:08:14.55,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就由我来带你成为大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.60,0:08:16.68,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.06,0:08:17.97,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你刚才有看我的胸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.39,0:08:19.43,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,色鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.52,0:08:20.23,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,人小鬼大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.35,0:08:25.65,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,了解以前的你的人  看到你现在的样子应该会吓到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.06,0:08:28.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,露科亚你不也一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.19,0:08:31.82,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,身为神明却安心当一个使魔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.11,0:08:34.49,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,因为这是我想做的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:36.45,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,所以不好好享受可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.49,0:08:38.12,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.70,0:08:40.50,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,翔太喜欢露科亚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.20,0:08:42.41,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你突然说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.54,0:08:44.67,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不是  我举个例子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.17,0:08:49.71,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,如果露科亚和你的朋友或是同学交好的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.21,0:08:52.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你看到这种场景  心情如何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.89,0:08:59.22,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,抱歉  你不想说也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:09:00.31,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不说也没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.60,0:09:05.02,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,也是呢  肯定会心有芥蒂的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.65,0:09:09.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.32,0:09:11.57,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,已经过去一小时了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.61,0:09:17.74,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.03,0:09:20.24,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我刚想说去找你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.79,0:09:21.83,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这浴衣很合适啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.37,0:09:23.50,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,谢谢夸奖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.12,0:09:26.50,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,大家在那边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.92,0:09:30.55,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,稍微…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:35.84,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我们两个人去转转吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.68,0:09:43.52,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,荣幸之至
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.85,0:09:46.69,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.48,0:09:51.48,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,难道终于理解托尔的魅力了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.44,0:09:54.49,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.03,0:09:58.36,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托尔是能和神明战斗的最强的龙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.99,0:10:02.33,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是只要愿意  也能和任何人搞好关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.20,0:10:07.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我之前听说了托尔以前的事  所以思考过了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.17,0:10:11.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我有资格被这样的人仰慕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.79,0:10:13.76,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你在想这种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.63,0:10:17.09,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我是不是说太多沉重的话了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.93,0:10:21.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,虽然现在已经是理所当然一样地在一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.10,0:10:23.97,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是想到托尔你背负的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.52,0:10:27.19,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,想到你毕竟是龙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.64,0:10:29.73,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就觉得这到底是什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.56,0:10:31.81,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这种想法一直在脑子里打转
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.27,0:10:33.07,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.40,0:10:36.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,算了吧  好麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.45,0:10:39.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,维持原状就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.66,0:10:44.66,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,虽然我得出了这样的结论
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.75,0:10:49.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是我想了解一下托尔你的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.71,0:10:51.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.34,0:10:55.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我喜欢小林
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.13,0:11:03.10,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是我知道我有很多比小林  比所有人类都优秀的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.93,0:11:06.89,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这是当然的  毕竟我是龙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.10,0:11:08.48,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,并且以此为荣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.19,0:11:13.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我也曾在堵上一切优胜劣汰的世界生活
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.57,0:11:18.65,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是心灵  心灵的优劣却无法评断
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.40,0:11:21.45,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,擅长战斗就代表优秀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.91,0:11:24.12,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,抑或是美貌与聪慧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.33,0:11:30.29,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我曾经不断朝着这些方向努力  不断祈愿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.08,0:11:32.75,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我想长大成人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.50,0:11:35.88,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是其实可以不用成为任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.55,0:11:38.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,保持自我就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.47,0:11:43.68,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是小林让我明白了这点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.89,0:11:47.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你还真会奉承我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.56,0:11:50.77,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林你可能没察觉到我有多高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.39,0:11:54.69,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,有人可以这么简单地拯救我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:11:57.32,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:11:59.44,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我最喜欢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.20,0:12:10.91,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,今后也一直  一直如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.48,0:12:38.23,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托尔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.98,0:12:39.48,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.82,0:12:41.40,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,太沉重了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.33,0:12:52.62,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你有之前夏日祭的照片吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.00,0:12:53.83,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.96,0:12:54.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,要看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.09,0:13:05.47,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我知道你们玩得很开心了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.89,0:13:06.51,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,对吧
Comment: 0,0:13:09.43,0:13:12.02,Kamisama S2 - Title,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(350,0)\pos(966.477,598.571)}最终话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.43,0:13:12.02,Kamisama S2 - Title,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(350,0)\pos(966.477,598.571)}生生不息（但偶尔驻足也不错）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.31,0:13:16.31,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,赏花吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.78,0:13:25.03,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,现在大夏天的你胡说些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.82,0:13:28.58,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我认识一个能把肉片变成鲜花的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.82,0:13:28.58,Kobayashi S2 - Comment,,0,0,0,,注：在阿兹特克神话中，女神索奇克察尔被割下私处的肉片，清洗后变成了鲜花。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.24,0:13:30.49,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,她分给了我一些
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.74,0:13:32.83,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但我一个人独享也没什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.46,0:13:35.71,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,肉片变鲜花？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.21,0:13:37.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这不是挺好的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.88,0:13:41.75,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就让我来主持一个能让小林开心的赏花大会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.05,0:13:43.84,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,为什么你这么积极啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.93,0:13:47.51,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,赏花不挺好的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.76,0:13:50.81,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我去加点素面酱汁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.86,0:14:00.57,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这就是肉片吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.90,0:14:02.44,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,虽然看起来只觉得是樱花
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.61,0:14:03.94,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:08.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,酒也带过来了  就开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.99,0:14:09.74,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.33,0:14:12.58,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那么恕我僭越
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.66,0:14:14.33,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就由身为活动负责人的我来说几句
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.12,0:14:19.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,由衷感谢各位来宾参加小林的赏花大会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.50,0:14:23.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,本次大会准备了诸多能让小林开心的娱乐项目
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.34,0:14:26.63,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,还请各位届时使出全力加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.76,0:14:29.09,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,会把我尴尬死的  所以别再说下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.89,0:14:37.69,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,樱饼好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.19,0:14:46.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,饶有风情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.03,0:14:50.53,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,一边喝着酒一边享受自然的满足度就是不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.99,0:14:53.70,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,享受自然？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.70,0:14:57.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就好像是在说人回归到自然中去的台词
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.58,0:14:59.67,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:02.09,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,在美的意识里追求客观性
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.13,0:15:04.50,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,两者共存的话就会变成这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.47,0:15:08.59,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这可真是煞风景
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.80,0:15:09.93,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你们是来干什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.05,0:15:12.55,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这也不失为一大乐趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.85,0:15:14.35,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,泷谷别分心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.60,0:15:16.22,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,打好配合断尾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.68,0:15:17.73,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.14,0:15:19.98,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,游戏内的信赖关系好深厚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.19,0:15:23.73,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,翔太君也是游戏派吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.98,0:15:27.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,因为全都是女孩子的话会坐立不安
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.03,0:15:28.95,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.15,0:15:31.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,少年怎么了  很闲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.20,0:15:31.70,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,艾尔玛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.78,0:15:32.41,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.66,0:15:35.74,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就让我露一手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.79,0:15:42.67,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.83,0:15:45.84,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好像在这种场合都会表演一下才艺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.38,0:15:47.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我查了很多资料
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.34,0:15:48.88,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,结果觉得这个就挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.97,0:15:50.55,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,做得挺精致的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.72,0:15:52.84,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,有专门表演这个的大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.05,0:15:54.05,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,让一个女孩子家演这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.81,0:15:56.64,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,非常吃这一套啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.89,0:15:57.52,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托尔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.02,0:16:00.31,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,太丑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.60,0:16:01.90,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,在另一个方面非常吃这一套
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.77,0:16:05.36,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,下次和才川玩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.48,0:16:07.48,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我也给翔太见识一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.57,0:16:08.94,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.44,0:16:12.11,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好了  气氛也炒起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.78,0:16:15.70,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,请抽签决定大赛的分组
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.58,0:16:17.33,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,大赛？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.83,0:16:19.25,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,扳手腕大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.00,0:16:22.25,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这个是你画的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.46,0:16:23.88,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托尔大人真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:26.50,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我不参加吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.92,0:16:28.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林是裁判
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.96,0:16:29.67,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,极好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.93,0:16:35.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,法夫纳也请
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.31,0:16:44.02,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好  那么第一战
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.85,0:16:46.23,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,泷谷对阵伊露露
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.07,0:16:48.32,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,泷谷你真的要上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.36,0:16:50.28,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,重在参与嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.86,0:16:52.20,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,算了  行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.78,0:16:54.53,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,预备
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.78,0:16:55.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,预备
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.16,0:16:57.33,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,开始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.83,0:17:06.88,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,可能骨折了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.96,0:17:09.55,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,居然只是骨折了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.00,0:17:10.88,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.42,0:17:13.84,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,没想到泷谷还挺莽撞的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.80,0:17:17.85,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好第二战是小康娜对阵露科亚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.85,0:17:19.97,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,准备
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.06,0:17:21.39,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,开始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.89,0:17:25.27,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,露科亚获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.69,0:17:27.44,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小康娜不能用两只手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.69,0:17:31.44,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,要来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:32.90,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.32,0:17:35.24,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,翔太君加油
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.39,0:18:01.10,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,只要再打败你  我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.02,0:18:06.10,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,先不说托尔  另一位赢到决赛的是露科亚阁下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.56,0:18:08.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我还以为是法夫哥留到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.36,0:18:10.23,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,别叫我法夫哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.11,0:18:13.23,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,因为宅久了身体迟钝了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.94,0:18:14.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,要你管
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.20,0:18:16.20,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这么说来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.70,0:18:17.70,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,虽然是玩玩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.91,0:18:20.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但还是第一次和你一对一单挑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.83,0:18:24.37,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,对你来说可能是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:26.25,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,认真一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.72,0:18:37.97,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好强
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.51,0:18:40.43,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,要输了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.35,0:18:44.22,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托尔小姐加油
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.18,0:18:46.27,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不是给我加油吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.10,0:18:48.27,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:53.32,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,获胜者  托尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:55.36,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.86,0:18:57.11,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托尔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.36,0:18:58.70,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不愧是她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.95,0:19:01.32,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,翔太君  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.62,0:19:02.66,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我收买了他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.78,0:19:03.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我被收买了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.04,0:19:05.33,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,给你  魔力水晶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.79,0:19:07.33,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.54,0:19:10.54,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,获胜者托尔是最佳女仆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.71,0:19:12.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.74,0:19:49.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林是真的喝得很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.21,0:19:51.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托尔也来一杯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.17,0:19:55.63,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那就恭敬不如从命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.51,0:20:05.26,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.68,0:20:07.02,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.14,0:20:09.60,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.27,0:20:11.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:14.94,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,太阳也快要下山了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.48,0:20:16.52,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.77,0:20:18.28,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,鼻子舞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.65,0:20:21.91,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,明天开始又要上班了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.16,0:20:24.49,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.78,0:20:26.33,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.58,0:20:28.91,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.45,0:20:31.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,今朝有酒今朝醉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.68,0:20:50.39,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.43,0:20:53.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,盛宴之时  酒过三巡了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.69,0:20:54.73,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我有不祥的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.15,0:20:56.15,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.90,0:20:58.27,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,在这落樱缤纷之下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.44,0:21:00.74,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,适逢诸位都在场
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.28,0:21:04.07,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,今日的压轴活动是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.91,0:21:06.12,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我托尔和…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.95,0:21:08.03,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.87,0:21:13.29,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,婚礼正式举行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.42,0:21:15.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.59,0:21:20.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.05,0:21:23.84,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,来吧  给小林换上嫁衣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.59,0:21:26.55,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.94,0:21:36.31,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,来吧  小林
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.28,0:21:43.90,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,请说「我爱你」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.08,0:21:59.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你是白痴吗
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/第一季OP
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.42,0:22:04.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.05,0:22:06.84,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,此般暴行岂能原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.05,0:22:08.39,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我要去救小林前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.35,0:22:10.64,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托尔大人犯规
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.39,0:22:13.73,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我也想和小林结为夫妻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.23,0:22:24.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,据魔力水晶所示
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.36,0:22:27.03,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这个婚礼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.24,0:22:29.37,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,祝福她们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.37,0:22:35.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,同事陷入危机可不能袖手旁观
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.50,0:22:40.29,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.05,0:22:48.01,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.47,0:22:49.64,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,现在可是身为龙的我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.05,0:22:53.97,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,效仿人类的价值观而举办的婚礼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.06,0:22:57.56,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但要是说不需要这种东西的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.77,0:22:59.60,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那也是可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.36,0:23:03.32,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你在自言自语些什么胡话  大蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.96,0:23:27.22,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我可不会让你逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.38,0:23:28.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林
