Comment: 0,0:23:29.34,0:23:35.01,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/完结
Dialogue: 1,0:23:36.22,0:23:38.52,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,本周堕落的是谁呢
Dialogue: 1,0:23:38.77,0:23:39.56,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,天秤座
