Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.55,0:22:02.42,Kabayashi S2 - EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}啾啾 yeah！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.05,0:22:05.97,Kabayashi S2 - EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}Please me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.64,0:22:09.51,Kabayashi S2 - EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}啾啾 yeah！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.10,0:22:13.14,Kabayashi S2 - EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}Without you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.94,0:22:21.36,Kabayashi S2 - EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}啊啊 怎么回事啦 细小的错误
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.48,0:22:24.78,Kabayashi S2 - EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}就弄得自己哒啦啦哒啦哒啦焦头烂额
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.99,0:22:28.45,Kabayashi S2 - EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}为何如此地突然  只要逃得远远就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.53,0:22:31.74,Kabayashi S2 - EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\an7}不知为何 又反复无常起来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.87,0:22:33.95,Kabayashi S2 - EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\an7}变成这样的感觉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.12,0:22:37.29,Kabayashi S2 - EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}一来就是这般感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.67,0:22:40.92,Kabayashi S2 - EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\an9}完全没有自己的模样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.29,0:22:46.01,Kabayashi S2 - EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\an9}但是如今推开那扇大门 就能听到声音啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.05,0:22:51.30,Kabayashi S2 - EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\an7}来 出发吧！（无论何处）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.64,0:22:58.35,Kabayashi S2 - EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\an9}我有成为你臂膀的勇气
